---
title: Tex-Mex Double Turkey Hash with Chipotle Mayo
description: Fancy some breakfast vibes for dinner tonight? Potatoes, hot peppers, corn and tomatoes are roasted to achieve beautiful caramelization before being tossed with turkey, onions and spices to create a heavenly hash.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R1010_W19_CA_RT156491-2_Main_low-d7a9391c.jpg
